deal.product_description: Bellroy leather phone case made specifically for the Google Pixel 8, constructed from premium Leather Working Group–rated leather with aluminum buttons for durability. The case offers a slim profile with a soft-lined interior to protect the phone, maintains wireless charging compatibility, and provides refined leather craftsmanship and edge protection while preserving phone functionality.

Roborock Qrevo Series QV 35S robot vacuum and mop with 10,000Pa suction, smart navigation and app control. The unit features a self‑emptying base, dynamic mopping, a dual anti‑tangle system to handle hair and debris, and onboard mapping for efficient room coverage. Model: QV 35S.

Roborock Q10 X5+ robot vacuum and mop with a self‑emptying dock, smart navigation and carpet detection. It offers up to 10,000 Pa of suction, obstacle avoidance and automated dirt disposal for hands‑off cleaning. The unit is designed to handle both vacuuming and mopping with intelligent pathing and app control for scheduling and settings.

A vertical standing LiFePO4 backup battery 4-pack providing 48V nominal output and 314Ah capacity per pack. Each module includes a 200A PACE BMS for protection, detachable terminals for flexible installation and expansion, and a built-in display for system monitoring. Designed for long cycle life (over 10,000 cycles with >80% DOD) for off-grid, backup power, or solar storage setups.
